structure Boo (α : Type) where
  a : α
  b : α
  c : α
example (a b d : Nat) (f : Nat → Boo Nat) : (f d).1 ≠ a → f d = ⟨b, v₁, v₂⟩ → b = a → False := by
  grind
def ex (a b c d : Nat) (f : Nat → Boo Nat) : (f d).2 ≠ a → f d = ⟨b, c, v₂⟩ → c = a → False := by
  grind
example (a b c : Nat) (f : Nat → Nat) : { a := f b, c, b := 4 : Boo Nat }
